OLD akx.9300.desc:0 "The [Root.GetName]'s name is being hailed... by the §HSyzygy§! of [Root.Owner.GetName]. This, despite the fact that it isn't sending any ID codes we recognize, and no ship of that name has ever been commissioned. The Syzygy's commanding officer claims to be Captain [mirrored_syzygy_admiral.GetName]."
NEW akx.9300.desc:1 "The [Root.GetName] is being hailed... by the "§HSyzygy§!" of the [Root.Owner.GetName]. This, despite the fact the "Syzygy" isn't sending any ID codes we recognize, and no ship of that name has ever been commissioned. Its commanding officer claims to be Captain §H[mirrored_syzygy_admiral.GetName]§!."
CN akx.9300.desc:1 "[Root.GetName]收到了来自于[Root.Owner.GetName]的§H朔望号§!的问候。然而，他们所发送来的身份号码无法识别，而我方也并没有一艘名为朔望号的舰船。朔望号的船长自称为船长[mirrored_syzygy_admiral.GetName]。"
CN2 akx.9300.desc:1 "[Root.Owner.GetName]的§H朔望号§!向[Root.GetName]致以问候。尽管我们无法从讯息中识别出任何符合的身份代码，记录在案的船只中也没有哪艘船是这个名字。朔望号的指挥官宣称自己是舰长§H[mirrored_syzygy_admiral.GetName]§!。"
