OLD akx.9319.desc:0 "A static-speckled message comes in from the captain of Syzygy, in [syzygy_location.GetStarName]. Behind them, the bridge is wreathed in smoke. §G"Too late,"§! they cough. §G"You left it too long. The Loop won't forgive me. Please -"§!\n\nThe message ends there."
